    "name": "破阵子",
    "steam_appid": 3296480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/1fdc7affcec751cf5fa1e0e9d3a12202.avif?t=1729833680\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras_big/1fdc7affcec751cf5fa1e0e9d3a12202.avif?t=1729833680 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破阵子是一款以刷为主的塔防游戏，玩家可以前往副本，关卡，各种活动性功能中，刷取道具，提高自己的战力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的职业系统，破阵子提供多种角色供玩家组合心目中的最强阵容（ps:职业会持续进行更新）。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/06a31cc16bcaeace001b48e9ee330be7.poster.avif?t=1729833680\" width=518 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/06a31cc16bcaeace001b48e9ee330be7.webm?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/06a31cc16bcaeace001b48e9ee330be7.mp4?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的养成系统，采用使用道具进行随机属性的方式，保证你的每个英雄的养成模式都不相同，定制属于自己的流派。例如，暴击流、减速流等。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/f4c92f0eb4090cfdc83c20bee94f4cf3.poster.avif?t=1729833680\" width=518 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/f4c92f0eb4090cfdc83c20bee94f4cf3.webm?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/f4c92f0eb4090cfdc83c20bee94f4cf3.mp4?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/90a17ffa379799c8ab043975e5f8de19.poster.avif?t=1729833680\" width=518 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/90a17ffa379799c8ab043975e5f8de19.webm?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/90a17ffa379799c8ab043975e5f8de19.mp4?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的道具系统和道具强化功能，超过上百种道具，供你使用。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/c6fe05332f216836e061e343852aa6b2.poster.avif?t=1729833680\" width=514 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/c6fe05332f216836e061e343852aa6b2.webm?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/c6fe05332f216836e061e343852aa6b2.mp4?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上百种不同路线的塔防关卡，你可以选择数值碾压（可能需要花更多的时间去刷道具），也可以利用你的智慧，去摆放合适的路径通关。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/52954d13f5d34f3ef5bd4628eef1e395.poster.avif?t=1729833680\" width=512 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/52954d13f5d34f3ef5bd4628eef1e395.webm?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/52954d13f5d34f3ef5bd4628eef1e395.mp4?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与人斗！其乐无穷！实时PVP，双方互相影响怪物路线！试想一下，对方的王牌被你的策略摆放导致连怪都打不到的乐趣！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/76e3d7a7a651d6f904868d9c1d755376.poster.avif?t=1729833680\" width=486 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/76e3d7a7a651d6f904868d9c1d755376.webm?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296480/extras/76e3d7a7a651d6f904868d9c1d755376.mp4?t=1729833680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
